OL,3,CCut PFAS chemicals in Jersey mains
OL,4,Cwater within five years, experts say
OL,6,FExperts are calling on Jersey's
OL,7,Fgovernment to cut the level of PFAS
OL,8,Fchemicals in the mains drinking water
OL,9,Fsupply within five years.
OL,11,FIn a draft interim report, the
OL,12,Findependent scientific advisory panel
OL,13,Frecommend that officials set a new,
OL,14,Flower combined limit for four key
OL,15,Ftypes of PFAS of 4ng/L.
OL,17,FHowever, they stress that Jersey
OL,18,FWater's public supply already meets UK
OL,19,Fand EU standards and there is no need
OL,20,Ffor panic.
