OL,6,FIn response, Jersey's government says
OL,7,Fit will study the findings.
OL,9,FEnvironment Minister, Deputy Steve
OL,10,FLuce, adds: "I want to thank the
OL,11,Fscientific panel for this detailed and
OL,12,Fhelpful report. I will consider their
OL,13,Ffindings and recommendations in detail
OL,14,Fso we can respond appropriately."
